2.plot: Curious about Blade and Soul? I count down the Top 5 Reasons to play Blade and Soul, while also giving you a bit of explanation for each reason. What is Blade and Soul? It is a free to play MMORPG by NC Soft that is brand new to us here in NA/EU, but has been out for a while in CH/KR/JP. Enjoy your possible first look at our Top 5 reasons we love the game! What are your reasons?
